{
  "stem": "12684.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How people in the whole, or as a whole, are capable of being alive, staying alive, being, quote-unquote, happy, knowing that every day can be-- next day can be doomsday, but to enjoy that you are alive-- alive today.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it's very, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] very interesting to see that in retrospect.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Because some of the things which you are confronted with were very sad, be it the dying people, be it the starving children, or people who suddenly lost their minds.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not the hard work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, everybody has to work for a living.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But that was the saddest thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I knew I wanted to be on my birthday on the palms.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That must have been in '44, in June.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were from Denmark and Swe-- and Sweden, and Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the whole camp was being, like, beautified for these people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know how many there were, maybe eight or 10.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And suddenly there were flowers, and there were better food.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And because you never know when they would be coming.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were just officers from these particular committees.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was confronted with them while I was working in the post office.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And for some reason-- I don't know, probably because I wore something red, they asked me questions that wasn't scheduled.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they kind of sat and stood-- half sat, half stood in front of me, and asked me all kinds of questions, which were [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] not leading-- leading questions, but you had to be very careful how to answer them.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And behind me was one of the SS guys, so I had to be sure to say the right thing because otherwise, I would be in the little prison.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
